# AI Features — Phase 14 (NOT NOW)

## Status: FUTURE — Do not implement business logic

All AI features are planned for Phase 14. When working on any AI-related file:
- Create the **stub/interface only**
- Mark every unimplemented method with `// TODO:AI - implement in Phase 14`
- Throw `AiNotAvailableException` in all methods
- Never install AI packages (openai-php, prism, etc.) until Phase 14

## Planned AI Features (Phase 14)
```
- AI proposal generator        → generate proposal content from project brief
- AI pricing suggestions       → suggest price ranges based on project type
- Auto form generator          → generate form fields from a description
- Project summarization        → summarize project activity + timeline
- AI usage tracking            → count + bill AI credits per company
```

## Stub Pattern — use this exactly
```php
<?php

namespace App\Domain\AI\Services;

use App\Exceptions\AiNotAvailableException;

/**
 * AI Proposal Generator
 *
 * TODO:AI - Implement in Phase 14
 * Will use OpenAI GPT-4o to generate proposal content from project data.
 */
class AiProposalService
{
    /**
     * Generate proposal content from a project brief.
     *
     * TODO:AI - implement in Phase 14
     * @throws AiNotAvailableException
     */
    public function generate(array $projectData): string
    {
        throw new AiNotAvailableException('AI features are not available yet.');
    }
}
```

## AiNotAvailableException
```php
class AiNotAvailableException extends \RuntimeException
{
    public function __construct(string $message = 'AI features coming soon.')
    {
        parent::__construct($message, 503);
    }
}
```

